OL,6,FA new drama, based on real notes kept
OL,7,Fby an consultant during the ,
OL,8,Fhighlights the fear and frustration
OL,9,Fthose on the frontline felt during the
OL,10,Fgreatest public health crisis in
OL,11,Fliving memory.
OL,13,FSet in a fictional big-city hospital,
OL,14,FBreathtaking follows Dr Abbey
OL,15,FHenderson - played by Golden Globe
OL,16,Faward-winning actress - in her daily
OL,17,Fwork as she tries to navigate the
OL,18,Fearly months of 2020.
