OL,6,FShe told ITV News: "The ethos behind
OL,7,Fthe drama is to make it the most
OL,8,Frealistic portrayal that we possibly
OL,9,Fcould.
OL,11,F"It's not just a re-telling of Covid,
OL,12,Fthis is the inside story of what was
OL,13,Freally happening behind the closed
OL,14,Fdoors of the hospitals - the story we
OL,15,Fas the public were fortunate enough
OL,16,Fnot to have dealings with."
