OL,6,FFor that reason, every patient case on
OL,7,Fthe show is based on a real person,
OL,8,Fand clips from the news and government
OL,9,Fpress conferences are woven in
OL,10,Fthroughout.
OL,12,FFroggatt, from and who is best known
OL,13,Ffor starring in Downtown Abbey,
OL,14,Fdescribed it as "surreal" having to
OL,15,Frevisit some of the things we all had
OL,16,Fto do during the pandemic, like
OL,17,Fwearing a face mask.
