OL,6,F"I realise for a lot of people it will
OL,7,Fbe incredibly triggering to watch
OL,8,Fdepending on their experiences during
OL,9,Fthe pandemic," she said, "but I would
OL,10,Furge people if they're able to, to
OL,11,Fplease not look away because this
OL,12,Fstory is a story we should all be
OL,13,Faware of."
OL,15,FThe three-part series has been adapted
OL,16,Ffor TV by writers Jed Mercurio (Line
OL,17,Fof Duty, Bodyguard, Trigger Point) and
OL,18,FPrasanna Puwanarajah, who are also
OL,19,Fboth former junior hospital doctors.
