OL,4,Cmemoir coming to ITV
OL,6,FDoctor-writer Rachel Clarke, whose
OL,7,Fmemoir of the same name inspired the
OL,8,Fseries, said: "There is so much
OL,9,Fmisinformation and rewriting of
OL,10,Fhistory around what really happened
OL,11,Finside our hospitals during the
OL,12,Fpandemic.
OL,14,F"The truth is, NHS staff gave
OL,15,Feverything they had in impossible
OL,16,Fconditions that sometimes cost them
OL,17,Ftheir lives.
