OL,6,F"It is an honour to try and depict the
OL,7,Fcourage and decency of my NHS
OL,8,Fcolleagues on screen, and I'm so
OL,9,Fgrateful to ITV and HTM Television for
OL,10,Fgiving me the chance to show the
OL,11,Fpublic the truth."
